                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5665" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0516</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8190 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大音希声——音书科技社创之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yinshu: Using science and technology to create “a blind path” for the hearing impaired</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘丹，郭翥璇，张倩，郑佩琰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京邮电大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">音书科技</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">科技发展部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">音书科技；社会企业；科技创新；听力言语障碍群体；技术风险；融资；可持续发展；2021百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yinshu Technology; Social enterprise; Scientific and technological innovation; Hearing and speech impairment group; Technical risk; Financing; sustainable development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">音书科技是一家科技创新型社会企业，致力于通过互联网+人工智能技术改善听力言语障碍群体的沟通现状。音书自主研发了听镜和语音翻译软件，为用户提供实时翻译服务。作为高科技的社会企业，技术研发和产品功能迭代都需要资金持续投入，但面向听障人士的公益服务性质却制约着音书的盈利性与商业价值。因此音书先后面临了来自于技术和资金的双重风险，创始团队不断寻求产品与市场突破，一次次冲出困境，努力实现企业的自我造血，在社会价值和经济价值之间的平衡中确保企业可持续发展。本案例通过描述音书科技社创之路，旨在引导同学们理解社会企业的概念，科技型社会创业在发展过程中的困境与解决方式，以及科技型社会企业的可持续发展路径。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Yinshu is a technological innovation oriented social enterprise, and is committed to improving the communication status of  hearing impaired groups through Internet + Artificial Intelligence. Yinshu independently developed “Tingjing” and language translation software to provide users with real-time translation services. As a high-tech social enterprise, the technology research and development and function iteration of products need continuous investment. However, the nature of public service for hearing-impaired people restricts the profitability and commercial value of  Yinshu. Therefore, Yinshu has faced double risks from technology and capital, the founding team constantly seeks product breakthrough and market breakthrough, strives to achieve corporate profitability, and ensures the sustainable development of the enterprise in the balance between social value and economic value. This case describes the road of social entrepreneurship of Yinshu, aiming to guide students to understand the concept of social enterprise, the difficulties and solutions in the development process of technological social entrepreneurship, and the sustainable development path of social enterprise.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创新与创业管理》、《社会创新与社会创业》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">社会企业、 社会创业概念范畴、 科技型企业创业特点、 社会企业可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-11</td>
                            </tr>
